name: SWISS A330 Business Class Review
description:
Join me for a "party" on this flight from Nairobi to Dar Es Salaam and on to Zurich. 

Was this Swiss Business Class excellent or terrible?

You'll see the seats, the food, the entertainment, and hear about the crew on this nighttime journey from Africa to Europe. And you can judge for yourself...

The SWISS A330 is the backbone of the SWISS International Air Lines fleet. The SWISS Business Class is beautiful, but how does it stack up on a nine hour flight.

This SWISS Airlines Flight Review also reveals what happens on the ground during a stopover in Dar Es Salaam, Tanzania.
